'''Proto-Georgian-Zan''' (also referred to as '''Proto-Karto-Zan''') is a [[reconstructed language]] which is the common ancestor of [[Karto-Zan languages]]. It had already branched out of the [[Proto-Kartvelian language]] during the last centuries of the 3rd millennium B.C.{{citation needed|date=July 2015}}

